## 🏗️ System Architecture Overview

### Database Architecture

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    MySQL Server                        │
├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                        │
│  ┌─────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────┐            │
│  │  stevedb        │    │  voltstartev_db │            │
│  │  (SteVe OCPP)   │    │  (VoltStartEV)  │            │
│  ├─────────────────┤    ├─────────────────┤            │
│  │ • charge_box    │    │ • users         │            │
│  │ • ocpp_tag      │    │ • charging_     │            │
│  │ • user_ocpp_tag │    │   sessions      │            │
│  │ • ocpp_tag_     │    │ • user_tags     │            │
│  │   activity(VIEW)│    │ • payments      │            │
│  │ • transaction_* │    │ • audit_logs    │            │
│  │ • connector_*   │    │                 │            │
│  │ • web_user      │    │                 │            │
│  └─────────────────┘    └─────────────────┘            │
│           │                        │                   │
│           │ Read-only              │ Read/Write        │
│           │ (via steveQuery)       │ (via appDb)       │
│           ▼                        ▼                   │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐           │
│  │      VoltStartEV Backend (Node.js)      │           │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘           │
│                                                        │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Key Architecture Points

| Component | Database | Access Type | Purpose |
|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| `ocpp_tag` | stevedb | Read-only | Tag validation |
| `ocpp_tag_activity` | stevedb | **VIEW (Read-only)** | Tag status (blocked, transaction count) |
| `user_ocpp_tag` | stevedb | Read/Write | User↔Tag linkage |
| `transaction_start/stop` | stevedb | Read-only | Transaction polling |
| `connector_meter_value` | stevedb | Read-only | Telemetry data |
| `charging_sessions` | voltstartev_db | Read/Write | Billing records |
| `users` | voltstartev_db | Read/Write | App user management |
| `user_tags` | voltstartev_db | Read/Write | User-friendly tag nicknames |

### Critical Notes for QA

| Finding | Impact on Testing |
|---------|------------------|
| `ocpp_tag_activity` is a **VIEW** | Cannot INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE directly; auto-updated by SteVe via OCPP messages |
| Tag blocking via **SteVe REST API** | Use `/api/v1/ocpp-tags/:idTag`, not direct SQL |
| `charging_sessions` has **generated columns** | Never INSERT/UPDATE `energy_kwh`, `total_cost`, `duration_seconds` |
| VoltStartEV writes only to `user_ocpp_tag` | Tag assignment tests focus on linkage table only |
| Transaction counts auto-update | Test must include OCPP StartTransaction/StopTransaction flows |

